; Name ..........: DoRevampSpells
; Description ...: Brewing full spells or revamp missing spells with what information get from CheckOnBrewUnit() And CheckAvailableSpellUnit()
;
; Syntax ........: DoRevampSpells()
; Parameters ....: $bDoPreTrain
;
; Return values .: None
; Author ........: Samkie (27 Jun 2017)
; Modified ......:
